-- SolarReserve-Led Group Wins South Africa Photovoltaic Contract
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2012-05-23T07:21:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-23/solarreserve-led-group-wins-south-africa-photovoltaic-contract.html
South Africa ’s Department of Energy
awarded an additional 88 megawatt photovoltaic project to a
group that includes SolarReserve LLC, the Kensani Group and
Intikon Energy, the companies said in a statement.  “This award brings the successful consortium’s award to
three projects totaling 238 megawatts and accounting for a 20
percent share of South Africa’s solar energy market,” the
companies said in a statement distributed by PR Newswire today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  